xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Okt 15, 2024</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent wide\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104naq1665702668499.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/naq1665702668499.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/naq1665702668499.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"naq1665702668499\" role=\"article\">\n<div class=\"body conbody\" id=\"naq1665702668499__setattributes_431216\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">Specify one or more session attributes and their values.</p>\n<section class=\"section refsyn\" id=\"naq1665702668499__topic_d131846e1_d131847e1_d131848e1\">\n<div class=\"p\">\n<div class=\"zDocsCodeExplanationContainer\"><button aria-label=\"Explain this code\" class=\"zDocsAiActionsButton\" data-target=\"#zDocsCodeExplanationModal_uniface_104naq1665702668499_html_0\" data-toggle=\"modal\" tabindex=\"0\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-code-explanation\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-code-explanation\"></use></svg>Explain this code</button></div><div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre codeblock language-plaintext\" data-explanation-rendered=\"true\" id=\"naq1665702668499__codeblock_pqy_mjd_dwb\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">$webinfo(\"SESSIONCOMMANDS\"), \"SetAttributes\",AttributeList</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n</div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"naq1665702668499__topic_d93627e1_d93628e1_d93629e1_d93630e1_d93631e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d858930e61\">Parameters</h2>\n<dl class=\"dl parml\" id=\"naq1665702668499__parml_drs_njd_dwb\">\n<dt class=\"dt pt dlterm\"><var class=\"keyword varname\">AttributeList</var></dt>\n<dd class=\"dd pd\">Associative list of one or more <code class=\"ph codeph\">\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">Attribute</var>=<var class=\"keyword varname\">Value</var>\n</code> pairs:\n                     <div class=\"zDocsCodeExplanationContainer\"><button aria-label=\"Explain this code\" class=\"zDocsAiActionsButton\" data-target=\"#zDocsCodeExplanationModal_uniface_104naq1665702668499_html_1\" data-toggle=\"modal\" tabindex=\"0\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-code-explanation\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-code-explanation\"></use></svg>Explain this code</button></div><div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre codeblock language-plaintext\" data-explanation-rendered=\"true\" id=\"naq1665702668499__codeblock_ugp_qjd_dwb\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">\"Attribute=Value {;Attribute=Value}\"</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div><ul class=\"ul\" id=\"naq1665702668499__ul_elr_rjd_dwb\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"naq1665702668499__li_d47219e1_d47220e1_d47221e1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"naq1665702668499__p_d131861e1_d131862e1_d131863e1\">\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">Attribute</var>—name of an session attribute;\n                           case-sensitive. If no attribute of that name exists, it is created.</p>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"naq1665702668499__li_d47222e1_d47223e1_d47224e1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"naq1665702668499__p_d131864e1_d131865e1_d131866e1\">\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">Value</var>—value of the session attribute.</p>\n</li>\n</ul></dd>\n</dl>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"naq1665702668499__topic_d93632e1_d93633e1_d93634e1_d93635e1_d93636e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d858930e111\">Description</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"naq1665702668499__p_d131870e1_d131871e1_d131872e1\">You can use the <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">SetAttributes</span>\n            command to associate additional information with the session.</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"naq1665702668499__p_d131873e1_d131874e1_d131875e1\">Session attributes are like variables that are\n            available on the WRD for the duration of the session. They can be used to share session\n            information between different server pages. For example, if a user has been\n            authenticated with a specific role, that information can be stored in as session\n            attribute and referenced by another component that needs to verify that the user has the\n            correct role. Or consider a web shop application—a search profile or shopping cart\n            contents can be stored in session attributes so that it is available to various server\n            pages the user accesses.</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"naq1665702668499__p_d131876e1_d131877e1_d131878e1\"><span class=\"keyword cmdname\">SetAttributes</span> is executed on the\n            current session. If the previous <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">ChangeSession</span> command was a\n               <code class=\"ph codeph\">CLOSE</code> action, the <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">SetAttributes</span> command is\n            ignored.</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"naq1665702668499__section_vdv_sjd_dwb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d858930e140\">Example: Defining and Setting Session Attributes</h2>\n<div class=\"p\">\n<div class=\"zDocsCodeExplanationContainer\"><button aria-label=\"Explain this code\" class=\"zDocsAiActionsButton\" data-target=\"#zDocsCodeExplanationModal_uniface_104naq1665702668499_html_2\" data-toggle=\"modal\" tabindex=\"0\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-code-explanation\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-code-explanation\"></use></svg>Explain this code</button></div><div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre codeblock language-plaintext\" data-explanation-rendered=\"true\" id=\"naq1665702668499__codeblock_c42_5jd_dwb\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">; Create a list of Session attributes and their values\nputitem/id vAttList, \"DATA1\", \"New\"\nputitem/id vAttList, \"Data2\", \"Edit\"\n; Add the command and its parameters to the SESSIONCOMMANDS chanel of $webinfo\nputitem/id $webinfo (\"SESSIONCOMMANDS\"), \"SetAttributes\" , vAttList</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n</div>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2530174\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2530174\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "SetAttributes Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Okt 15, 2024 Summarize Uniface 10.4 Specify one or more session attributes and their values. Explain this code $webinfo(\"SESSIONCOMMANDS\"), \"SetAttributes\",AttributeList Copy Parameters AttributeList Associative list of one or more Attribute = Value pairs: Explain this code \"Attribute=Value {;Attribute=Value}\" Copy Attribute —name of an session attribute; case-sensitive. If no attribute of that name exists, it is created. Value —value of the session attribute. Description You can use the SetAttributes command to associate additional information with the session. Session attributes are like variables that are available on the WRD for the duration of the session. They can be used to share session information between different server pages. For example, if a user has been authenticated with a specific role, that information can be stored in as session attribute and referenced by another component that needs to verify that the user has the correct role. Or consider a web shop application—a search profile or shopping cart contents can be stored in session attributes so that it is available to various server pages the user accesses. SetAttributes is executed on the current session. If the previous ChangeSession command was a CLOSE action, the SetAttributes command is ignored. Example: Defining and Setting Session Attributes Explain this code ; Create a list of Session attributes and their values putitem/id vAttList, \"DATA1\", \"New\" putitem/id vAttList, \"Data2\", \"Edit\" ; Add the command and its parameters to the SESSIONCOMMANDS chanel of $webinfo putitem/id $webinfo (\"SESSIONCOMMANDS\"), \"SetAttributes\" , vAttList Copy Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}